Beskrivelse: [ Dansk Engelsk ]

All episodes from the ninth season of the award-winning US drama following the lives of medical professionals in the fictional Seattle Grace Mercy West Hospital. In this series, the hospital staff try to overcome the tragic consequences of the plane crash which took place in the previous season.
